(firstQuint)GER-009-06-AVX Early Therapy in Multiple Sclerosis.

 This study will address the cognitive dysfunction associated with MS.

 It will track these changes and show that early intervention with Avonex is effective in slowing MS and its effect on patients.

 Safety data will also be collected during this study.

